  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to evaluate the efficacy of an intensive handwriting treatment in
      Parkinson's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aimed to understand whether an intensive handwriting treatment with
      cognitive engagement is more effective than a treatment exploiting only the passive wrist
      joint mobilization in Parkinson's Disease.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
